{"tid":1726334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗韓國戰線，越南都好值得做","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T14:36:50.000Z","uid":4574,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"229a17190f496cd01ee3d74b4a0decb97aab1a53","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/phongtraoduvanghongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphongtraoduvanghongkong%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=07dc8f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/phongtraoduvanghongkong/</a><br />\n呢個page有五萬人 好多活躍用戶<br />\n佢哋對香港有興趣 時事更得貼<br />\n<br />\n1）多靚女 eg Elly Tran 阮金紅<br />\n2）支那千年世仇<br />\n3）一億人口 新興經濟體<br />\n4）香港幫助過越南難民<br />\n5）地理位置、歷史淵源近，幫過胡志明、保大帝<br />\n6）香港有唔少越南人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQqSbUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQqSbUL.jpg&h=27b84d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連登有無手足識越南話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a66f0387de76159342165fd68674c55ebbca52f","tid":1726334,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"不漏洞奶"},{"pid":"c34a204361f88464b844d263750cbca3a9c35317","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d88793734158368c2a7c7abc1a6c711e43fc42d","tid":1726334,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=ced51a6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=80c1cffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"ef230397661ab9df9172f91b5f897cb4751d399c","tid":1726334,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"不嬲覺得香港人如果將早年支援支那工商業果種熱情完全投入到越南<br />\n越南唔會今時今日都咁落後<br />\n香港亦唔會過份依賴支那<br />\n根本係雙贏<br />\n不過越南同香港溝通難過支那<br />\n係一個大問題"},{"pid":"2d35ee5e0249b33f041e6917bbf38a889643d12f","tid":1726334,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"熟熟地越南<br />\n<br />\n越南共產黨 將 香港反送中戰鬥 定義為 爭取獨立既戰爭<br />\n所以官方媒體描述香港嘅事大概同新加坡差唔多<br />\n但係當地人有得睇cnn bbc 嘅野<br />\n所以越南讀過大學個班 高等人可能會有唔同嘅諗法 <br />\n<br />\n不過我唔認為果邊嘅華人社會係助力<br />\n<br />\n當地人唔鐘意中國人<br />\n但係佢地分唔出香港同中國嘅分別<br />\n大家入境越南既時候都係一概當中國人<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n個邊好多南韓 同台灣人<br />\n日本人中國人都唔少"},{"pid":"620eafb279a85efb425ec33262c742ee9a854df8","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d35ee5e0249b33f041e6917bbf38a889643d12f","tid":1726334,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"熟熟地越南<br />\n<br />\n越南共產黨 將 香港反送中戰鬥 定義為 爭取獨立既戰爭<br />\n所以官方媒體描述香港嘅事大概同新加坡差唔多<br />\n但係當地人有得睇cnn bbc 嘅野<br />\n所以越南讀過大學個班 高等人可能會有唔同嘅諗法 <br />\n<br />\n不過我唔認為果邊嘅華人社會係助力<br />\n<br />\n當地人唔鐘意中國人<br />\n但係佢地分唔出香港同中國嘅分別<br />\n大家入境越南既時候都係一概當中國人<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n個邊好多南韓 同台灣人<br />\n日本人中國人都唔少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"Ching識嘢<br />\n<br />\n早幾年越南排華<br />\n啲支那狗無恥到<br />\n掛青天白日旗<br />\n<br />\n加強宣傳 有無得做？"},{"pid":"058c97bfe9f3ff39f9363c257894436c83020ce9","tid":1726334,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:54:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6dac413cd7cfd6e65d2787c3cdd1f9ea342e2bf","tid":1726334,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"229a17190f496cd01ee3d74b4a0decb97aab1a53","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/phongtraoduvanghongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphongtraoduvanghongkong%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=07dc8f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/phongtraoduvanghongkong/</a><br />\n呢個page有五萬人 好多活躍用戶<br />\n佢哋對香港有興趣 時事更得貼<br />\n<br />\n1）多靚女 eg Elly Tran 阮金紅<br />\n2）支那千年世仇<br />\n3）一億人口 新興經濟體<br />\n4）香港幫助過越南難民<br />\n5）地理位置、歷史淵源近，幫過胡志明、保大帝<br />\n6）香港有唔少越南人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQqSbUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQqSbUL.jpg&h=27b84d98&s={SIZE}