立既戰爭<br />\n所以官方媒體描述香港嘅事大概同新加坡差唔多<br />\n但係當地人有得睇cnn bbc 嘅野<br />\n所以越南讀過大學個班 高等人可能會有唔同嘅諗法 <br />\n<br />\n不過我唔認為果邊嘅華人社會係助力<br />\n<br />\n當地人唔鐘意中國人<br />\n但係佢地分唔出香港同中國嘅分別<br />\n大家入境越南既時候都係一概當中國人<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n個邊好多南韓 同台灣人<br />\n日本人中國人都唔少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"Ching識嘢<br />\n<br />\n早幾年越南排華<br />\n啲支那狗無恥到<br />\n掛青天白日旗<br />\n<br />\n加強宣傳 有無得做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"越南而家食緊中國人血饅頭<br />\n加埋處於上升期<br />\n未必有人會理我地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"或者港資轉去 <br />\n越南發展？"},{"pid":"5cc3788df8f49b27b9cd4bc41ad7a4a0ea0c77ce","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不漏洞奶</blockquote>漏奶咩撚關係</blockquote>"},{"pid":"abcac1eba87d40ed4cda02490e388dd32363eca1","tid":1726334,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"69584acbc95e1d1273962b33e06cdba896f95768","tid":1726334,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"但唔識越南文點搞"},{"pid":"0d1c5ca6416472ef025f0604196ace170fa608c9","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69584acbc95e1d1273962b33e06cdba896f95768","tid":1726334,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"但唔識越南文點搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"連登手足有父母<br />\n其中一邊係越南人"},{"pid":"3e1633f9951afffc22865cc9039c1dced4033462","tid":1726334,"uid":265731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"可以一試但唔好抱太大期望<br />\n<br />\n越南同中國唔妥好耐，新仇舊恨斷斷續續都有軍事衝突。都俾人恰咗咁耐，但唔夠力還拖。經濟上，大家都知道喺中國嘅工廠呢幾年大規模遷移去東南亞，越南食唔少，佢地當然想中國衰多兩錢重，等更多嘅錢流入啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，越南都係共產國家。雖然而家資訊開放，但民智唔係好開，入到去都係講錢。而家養肥佢同當年養肥中國一樣，好易養虎遺患。再加上，以佢地而家嘅國力，都未足以阻擋到中國，而家頂多都係推波助瀾。<br />\n<br />\n呢條戰線都係加小小文宣就算"},{"pid":"c06f7b7b8f2deb75d83913f1cb24f26a7cc103c7","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"c62438ae6f832918be58019326f80acb602f454f","tid":1726334,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2672fbf9eb234f3907a3e6c7dedd2a1845c67b45","tid":1726334,"uid":178272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/500089374090858/permalink/551177322315396?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F500089374090858%2Fpermalink%2F551177322315396%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=f1f9f593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/500089374090858/permalink/551177322315396?sfns=mo</a><br />\n來自越南的支持😭"},{"pid":"1b562da1060f8856ff2e5b20f3994cf22e6ed0ab","tid":1726334,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"有波真係好正"},{"pid":"1f5bbd51a716b6cfa6dfb210508e26a0b6cb43cc","tid":1726334,"uid":257885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n好多越南人其實好support香港<br />\n但其實之前佢哋未必好分得清楚香港同支那<br />\n利申：多越南fd"},{"pid":"058a2defb241f90985265e93283fb14cead66d01","tid":1726334,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f5bbd51a716b6cfa6dfb210508e26a0b6cb43cc","tid":1726334,"uid":257885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n好多越南人其實好support香港<br />\n但其實之前佢哋未必好分得清楚香港同支那<br />\n利申：多越南fd"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"香港有部分人樣似南越人<br />\n<br />